name: Emily Takes On Winner's
description:
You play as Emily, local Goth Girl and Spencer's Employee. You have a burning hatred for Winner's and it's customers, and you'll do whatever it takes to bring down the Winner's franchise in this tense Wave Shooter.

Why did I make this? Not really sure. It's not a good game, and it took me like, 2 hours to make, but it's here anyways because I feel like the world needs to see this.
